XI. SYNTHESIS ELIGIBILITY RULE

Synthesis only allowed when:

≥ 20 stable primitives.

No unresolved break conflicts.

Transfer mapping performed on ≥ 30% of primitives.

At least 2 contradiction attempts documented.

If not satisfied:
Remain in extraction mode.

